  "detailed_description": "<strong>League of Pixels is a fast paced pixel art approach on the MOBA genre, where you don't have to spend 30+ minutes to complete one game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198760/extras/81ff720e8a2c1de9883f4b1ffc7c0a63.avif?t=1610547376\" width=230 height=86 /></span><br><br>Choose one of many different characters from a constantly rising roster, eliminate the enemy player and destroy the base to gain victory!<br>Average games take 5-10 minutes, so you don't have to worry about spending too much time in one game.<br><br><i>The game is free to play, and every gameplay related content is available right from the start. You won't need to grind for Characters!</i><br><br>You can decide to play in Online Multiplayer, Local Splitscreen or in Singleplayer, so there is always the right mode for any situation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198760/extras/20ced0570d5696a73bbdf6325570e5af.avif?t=1610547376\" width=460 height=214 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>League of Pixels is a fast paced pixel art approach on the MOBA genre, where you don't have to spend 30+ minutes to complete one game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198760/extras/81ff720e8a2c1de9883f4b1ffc7c0a63.avif?t=1610547376\" width=230 height=86 /></span><br><br>Choose one of many different characters from a constantly rising roster, eliminate the enemy player and destroy the base to gain victory!<br>Average games take 5-10 minutes, so you don't have to worry about spending too much time in one game.<br><br><i>The game is free to play, and every gameplay related content is available right from the start. You won't need to grind for Characters!</i><br><br>You can decide to play in Online Multiplayer, Local Splitscreen or in Singleplayer, so there is always the right mode for any situation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198760/extras/20ced0570d5696a73bbdf6325570e5af.avif?t=1610547376\" width=460 height=214 /></span>",
